&lt;li&gt;Identify, qualify, and execute opportunities to expand MixMode into new government branches and sectors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own customer relationships from first contact to contract award&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with fellow team members (solutions, contracting, product, program management) to deliver exceptional support to prospective customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and track sales metrics within our customer relationship management system to enhance company forecasting capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute a consultative sales process that aligns the value of our software product with the needs of an organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a player/coach with future people management opportunities as the MixMode sales team scales&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support solutions and contracting team with proposal and presentation material creation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
